Class EPPSuggestionTst

junit.framework.Test
public class EPPSuggestionTst
extends junit.framework.TestCase

Is a unit test of the EPPSuggestion class. The unit test will initialize a session with an EPP Server, will invoke EPPSuggestion operations, and will end a session with an EPP Server. The configuration file used by the unit test defaults to epp.config, but can be changed by passing the file path as the first command line argument. The unit test can be run in multiple threads by setting the "threads" system property. For example, the unit test can be run in 2 threads with the configuration file ../../epp.config with the following command:

java com.verisign.epp.interfaces.EPPSuggestionTst -Dthreads=2 ../../epp.config

The unit test is dependent on the use of JUNIT 3.5
